data.description:
Nestled on a serene half-acre parcel within the picturesque Rust Ranches, this 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom modular home offers a tranquil escape while maintaining easy access to a wealth of nearby amenities. The sprawling property boasts the best of both worlds, with a perfect blend of rural tranquility and urban convenience.
This well-maintained modular home has been thoughtfully designed to provide a comfortable and efficient living space. The four bedrooms offer ample room for family and guests, while the open-concept kitchen and living area provide a warm and inviting atmosphere. Modern appliances and fixtures enhance the functionality of this charming home, creating a space that's perfect for both relaxation and entertaining.
The half-acre lot offers a canvas for personalization, whether it's creating a lush garden oasis, building a spacious deck for outdoor gatherings. The possibilities are endless.
Rust Ranches is a neighborhood, strategically situated to provide easy access to nearby towns and attractions. Blanco, with its rich history and charming town square, is just minutes away. The scenic beauty of Canyon Lake and the entire Hill Country area are at your fingertips, allowing you to explore hiking, boating, and the natural wonders of the region.
Whether you're seeking a peaceful retreat or a convenient hub for exploring the Hill Country, this 4/2 modular home on half an acre in Rust Ranches delivers on both fronts. It's a place where rural serenity meets modern comfort, ensuring that you can savor the best of Texas living in a prime location.
